        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Head Quarters</placeName>,<date when="1835-11-06"> Novr 6th 1835</date></p>

<p>To the <persName>Commander in chief of the army of <placeName>Texas</placeName></persName></p>

<p>Sir&#8212; Believing that I can not be longer useful to the <persName>army </persName>without 
complaints being made, I herewith tender to your Excellency my resignation
as <persName>Capt. of Cavalry</persName>&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>W. B. Travis</persName></p>


        </div1>
